column5: Wow!  Awesome piece of machinery there!   I especially like how you can run it up to the beach then the "grabbers" cant pull you in a little closer.  Awesome!

My neighbour at the lake has a landing craft. It was awesome for bringing out materials and he also hauled his side by side out with it. Lots of guys in Alaska use them. They are excellent for hunting and they can bring their quads out with them.
